sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / SDK
    participant UI as ml-pipeline-ui<br/>3000/TCP HTTP
    participant API as ml-pipeline API Server<br/>8888/TCP HTTP<br/>8887/TCP gRPC
    participant DB as MySQL/PostgreSQL<br/>3306/5432 TCP
    participant S3 as MinIO/S3<br/>9000/443 TCP
    participant K8s as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Argo as Argo Workflow Controller
    participant Driver as kfp-driver<br/>(init container)
    participant Launcher as kfp-launcher
    participant MLMD as metadata-grpc-server<br/>8080/TCP gRPC
    participant Envoy as metadata-envoy<br/>9090/TCP gRPC-Web
    participant Cache as cache-server<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant PA as persistenceagent
    participant SW as scheduledworkflow

    Note over User,S3: Flow 1: Pipeline Submission and Execution

    User->>API: POST /apis/v2beta1/pipelines/upload<br/>Bearer Token
    API->>DB: Store pipeline metadata<br/>Username/Password
    API->>S3: Store pipeline artifacts<br/>Access Key/Secret
    API->>K8s: Create Workflow CR<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    K8s->>Argo: Workflow scheduled
    Argo->>Driver: Init container starts
    Driver->>API: gRPC :8887<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    Driver->>MLMD: gRPC :8080<br/>plaintext
    Launcher->>S3: Upload artifacts<br/>Access Key/Secret

    Note over User,S3: Flow 2: Persistence Agent Status Sync

    PA->>K8s: Watch Workflows<br/>HTTPS/TLS<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    PA->>API: Report status<br/>gRPC :8887<br/>Projected SA Token

    Note over User,S3: Flow 3: Scheduled Workflow Execution

    SW->>K8s: Watch ScheduledWorkflow CRs<br/>HTTPS/TLS<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    SW->>API: Create Run<br/>gRPC :8887<br/>Projected SA Token

    Note over User,S3: Flow 4: Cache Evaluation

    K8s->>Cache: Pod admission webhook<br/>HTTPS :8443<br/>mTLS
    Cache->>DB: Check cache<br/>Username/Password

    Note over User,S3: Flow 5: Frontend UI Access

    User->>UI: HTTP :3000<br/>Platform auth
    UI->>API: HTTP :8888<br/>Forwarded identity header
    UI->>Envoy: gRPC-Web :9090<br/>plaintext
    Envoy->>MLMD: gRPC :8080<br/>plaintext
